    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 41-7-191, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO DIRECT THE STATE DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH TO ISSUE A CERTIFICATE OF NEED TO A NONPROFIT CORPORATION LOCATED IN MADISON COUNTY FOR THE CONSTRUCTION, EXPANSION OR CONVERSION OF ADDITIONAL BEDS IN A COMMUNITY LIVING PROGRAM FOR DEVELOPMENTALLY DISABLED ADULTS IN AN ICF-IID FACILITY; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
